IG and beautiful cocktail rings are the ultimate accessory that draw attention to your hands, whether you are wearing a colourful, whimsical dress or a little black dress. There are so many rings to choose from, ranging from the bold and crazily crafted to the bling-bling. A simple, yet elegant cocktail ring is basically defined as an oversized rock design with precious coloured stones. For you to make a statement with your cocktail ring, it has to be chunky (bold), and at the same time stylish. This is the ultimate cocktail ring golden rule. Believe it, the big rock is a solid way to highlight your individual style. You can never go wrong with one. Get as many as possible with different hues. You can wear a different one for each day; it all depends on your attire. They are the classic and timeless finger pieces.